headline: Waters Corporation to Present at the Wells Fargo Healthcare Conference
summary: Waters Corporation (NYSE:WAT) announced that Udit Batra, Ph.D., Waters President and Chief Executive Officer, will participate in a fireside chat at the Wells Fargo Healthcare Conference on Thursday, September 4th, 2025, at 9:30 AM Eastern Time.
